value.0: Hello and welcome to the Last Jedi!

In order to enter the server you must first choose an appropriate race. Please remake your character to one of the following: Half-Orc Male, Human Male or Female, Elf Male or Female. Once you have an appropriate character you may speak to me again to choose a subrace and enter the server.

You have chosen to play as one of the species available to the Elf. Note: If you do not see the species you wish to play as here, it may fall under the category of human or half-orc. Select Done once you have made a decision.
You have chosen to play as a Wookiee, which head would you like to pick? Select Done once you have made a decision.

You have chosen to play as a Human, however, you may select a new species if you wish. Note: If you do not see the species you wish to play as here, it may fall under the category of elf or half-orc. Once you have made a decision select Done.
To make certain species truly unique and represent how rare they are in the Galaxy, you must attain special DM permission before you are able to create a character with them.
If you would like to use one of the new voice sets available, please feel free to try them out and select continue when you are done. You can use the V commands to test the voices.
Please choose a skin colour for your subrace. When you are happy with a colour, please select done.
